record_data.record_plain_text:
Southern Indiana Gas & Electric Company
Reactive Supply and Voltage Control from Generation or Other Sources Service Southern Indiana Gas & Electric Company ("SIGECo") provides Reactive Supply and Voltage Control from Generation Sources Service ("Reactive Power Service") from facilities located in the Midcontinent Independent System Operator, Inc. ("MISO") transmission footprint. This Rate Schedule sets forth SIGECo's revenue requirements for the provision of Reactive Power Service from the facilities listed below in accordance with Schedule 2 to the MISO Open Access Transmission, Energy and Operating Reserve Markets Tariff. Annual and monthly revenue requirements for the specified facilities and total fleet-wide annual and monthly revenue requirements are set forth below:
